Package: micEconDistRay
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2023-04-09
Title: Econometric Production Analysis with Ray-Based Distance Functions
Authors@R: c( person( "Arne", "Henningsen", role = c( "aut", "cre" ), 
    email = "arne.henningsen@gmail.com" ),
  person( "Juan JosÃ©", "Price", role = c( "aut" ) ) )
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports: sfaR (>= 1.0), stats (>= 4.2.0)
Description: Tools for econometric analysis 
   of multiple-input-multiple-output production technologies
   with ray-based input distance functions
   as suggested by Price and Henningsen (2022): 
   "A Ray-Based Input Distance Function to Model Zero-Valued Output Quantities: 
   Derivation and an Empirical Application",
   <https://ideas.repec.org/p/foi/wpaper/2022_03.html>.
